0506               * Put length-byte prefixed string at YX
0507               ***************************************************************
0508               *  BL   @PUTAT
0509               *  DATA P0,P1
0510               *
0511               *  P0 = YX position
0512               *  P1 = Pointer to string
0513               *--------------------------------------------------------------
