0038               
0039 3596 8806  34         c     tmp2,@parm2           ; String length > requested length?
     3598 A014     
0040 359A 1520  14         jgt   tv.pad.string.panic   ; Yes, crash
0041                       ;------------------------------------------------------
0042                       ; Copy string to buffer
